Author: Erik LaBianca <erik.labianca@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu May 14 05:48:42 2026 -0400

    chore: remove checked-in DDx skill mirrors [ddx-11ef34e1]

    `.agents/skills/ddx`, `.claude/skills/ddx`, and `.ddx/skills/ddx` are now
    produced by the embedded package installer (`ddx init`) or the local
    overlay (`ddx plugin install ddx --local library --force`), not edited as
    source. The canonical source is `library/skills/ddx` and the embedded
    binary copy is `cli/internal/registry/defaultplugin/library/`.

    Drop the hard-coded `.agents/skills` fallback in the local install path
    when the manifest declares an explicit `install.skills[*].source` so
    `--local library` installs from `library/skills/` instead of
    `library/.agents/skills/` (plan-2026-05-13).

